@startuml

title Section 18.2 - Iteration 1 Security Hardening
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor Customer
actor Staff

component "API Gateway" as gateway
component "Identity Service\nJWT + RBAC" as identity
component "Django Web App" as django
component "Payment Service" as payment
component "Shipping Service" as shipping

Customer --> gateway
Staff --> gateway
gateway --> identity : token validation
gateway --> django : authorized request
gateway --> payment : service route
gateway --> shipping : service route
identity --> django : claims propagation

note bottom of identity
Adds authentication + role checks
for customer/staff operations.
end note

@enduml
